  "texts": [
    "This way CNN features can be simply supplemented with selected hand-engineered features before classification (see e.g.",
    "Orenstein and Beijbom 2017; Keçeli et al. 2017).",
    "Similarly, ensembles of classifiers can be utilized to combine handcrafted feature based classification and CNNs.",
    "For example, in the method proposed by Lumini and Nanni (2019a); Lumini et al. (2020) individual classifiers utilized in the ensembles included various CNNs applied to both original images and preprocessed (filtered) images.",
    "The preprocessing techniques included various filters commonly used to compute local features, such as gradient, LBP and wavelets."
  ],
